      <description>&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Projects&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;projects&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#projects&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;PTS UI &amp;amp;&amp;amp; SERVICE&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;pts-ui--service&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#pts-ui--service&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;DCTR SERVICE CI&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;dctr-service-ci&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#dctr-service-ci&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;HMBS BRE SERVICE&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;hmbs-bre-service&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#hmbs-bre-service&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;RECERTIFICATION SERVICE&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;recertification-service&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#recertification-service&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;HUD11708 SERVICE&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;hud11708-service&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#hud11708-service&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;BATCH JOB&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;batch-job&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#batch-job&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Challenges&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;challenges&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#challenges&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Virtual thread block the other thread&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;virtual-thread-block-the-other-thread&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#virtual-thread-block-the-other-thread&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;jps -l&lt;/code&gt; # to list java process, find springboot Application.class process&#xA;2.0 &lt;code&gt;jcmd 12345 help&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;jcmd 12345 Thread.print&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- 2.legacy jstack 12345 # thread dump, to debug thead deadlock, stuck threads: look for BLOCKED, and WAITING threads --&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol start=&#34;3&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;jcmd 12345 VM.flags&lt;/code&gt; # inspect JVM flags&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;jcmd 12345 GC.heap_info&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- 4.legacy jmap -heap 12345 # memory dump, to debug memory leak --&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol start=&#34;5&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;jcmd PID VM.command_line&lt;/code&gt; # inspect JVM arguments&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- 5.legacy `wmic process where processid=12345 get commandline` --&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Use JFR&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;use-jfr&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#use-jfr&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;jcmd 12345 JFR.start name=debug duration=60s filename=C:\temp\debug.jfr&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;1.1 &lt;code&gt;jcmd JFR.check&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;1.2 &lt;code&gt;jcmd JFR.stop name=xxx&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;jmc&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;BRE performance: stream dao layer for large query, separate query to avoid large CTE, virtual thread&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;bre-performance-stream-dao-layer-for-large-query-separate-query-to-avoid-large-cte-virtual-thread&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#bre-performance-stream-dao-layer-for-large-query-separate-query-to-avoid-large-cte-virtual-thread&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Production defect: WAF rule&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;production-defect-waf-rule&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#production-defect-waf-rule&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;DB Unique index constraint bug for efficient code&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;db-unique-index-constraint-bug-for-efficient-code&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#db-unique-index-constraint-bug-for-efficient-code&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Drool syntax: &amp;amp;&amp;amp; cannot skip second part, comma can skip second part&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;drool-syntax--cannot-skip-second-part-comma-can-skip-second-part&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#drool-syntax--cannot-skip-second-part-comma-can-skip-second-part&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Not code related: not coding error, need to push back to not coding error&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;not-code-related-not-coding-error-need-to-push-back-to-not-coding-error&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#not-code-related-not-coding-error-need-to-push-back-to-not-coding-error&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;jdk25 bugs:&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;jdk25-bugs&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#jdk25-bugs&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol start=&#34;2&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;jackson 3, cannot use primitive boolean in payload&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;sb4 bugs:&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;sb4-bugs&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#sb4-bugs&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;queryForObject always throw EmptyResultDataAccessException if set fetchSize globally, we should use for each preparedStatement for each query&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;improve query performance&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;improve-query-performance&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#improve-query-performance&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;reduce the size of CTE (common table expression)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;landing on index (most of time)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;improve table join&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Experience&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;experience&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#experience&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;TA&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;ta&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#ta&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;2022 Spring: Data structure &amp;amp; algorithms by Calvin Lin&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;2025 Spring: Advances in Deep Learning by Philipp Krahenbuhl&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;2025 Summer: Advances in Deep Learning by Philipp Krahenbuhl&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;2025 Fall: Natural Language Processing by Greg Durrett &amp;amp; Jessy Li&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;2026 Spring: Advances in Generative Modeling by Qiang Liu&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Staff SDE&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;staff-sde&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#staff-sde&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;leading cross-team initiatives, writing design docs others reference, and mentoring&#xA;might make a lateral Senior move into a more ML-adjacent role at your current level, then grow into ML-infra-specialized Staff over 2-3 years.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
